### (6) The Adulterer.

<span class="margnote">**M**.</span>6*b*. He who has criminal connexion
with a man's wife: that is, at a time when the woman, after the
marriage, has come under the control of the husband. Even though the
marriage be not consummated, if he have criminal connexion with her, he
is to be strangled.

